      <title>中国反对日本首相参拜靖国神社</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-opposes-japan-prime-ministers-offering-yasukuni-shrine-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国周一对日本首相岸田文雄在东京一座有争议的神社进行祭祀表示强烈反对，中国和韩国认为该神社是日本过去军事侵略的象征。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-opposes-japan-prime-ministers-offering-yasukuni-shrine-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 08:12:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国梦的破灭迫使西方金融公司削减成本</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/souring-china-dreams-force-western-financial-firms-cut-costs-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在几年前，中国经济蓬勃发展带来的利润丰厚的商业前景导致西方金融公司（从投资银行到资产管理）竞相扩大业务范围并从世界各地招募人才。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/souring-china-dreams-force-western-financial-firms-cut-costs-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 07:42:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗总统抵达巴基斯坦进行为期三天的访问以修复关系</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/iranian-president-lands-pakistan-three-day-visit-mend-ties-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[外交部表示，在巴基斯坦首都戒备森严的情况下，伊朗总统易卜拉欣·莱西周一抵达伊斯兰堡，开始为期三天的正式访问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/iranian-president-lands-pakistan-three-day-visit-mend-ties-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 07:12:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报告称朝鲜人可能帮助创作了西方漫画</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreans-may-have-helped-create-western-cartoons-report-says-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份研究报告发现，尽管国际社会对朝鲜实施了制裁，朝鲜动画师可能还是帮助亚马逊和 HBO Max 等西方大公司创作了受欢迎的电视动画片。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreans-may-have-helped-create-western-cartoons-report-says-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 07:05:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度尼西亚法院驳回寻求重新选举的两项请愿书中的第一项</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesian-court-rejects-first-two-petitions-seeking-election-re-run-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚一家法院周一完全驳回了落选候选人阿尼斯·巴斯韦丹 (Anies Baswedan) 提出的要求重新参加二月总统选举的挑战，并取消了获胜者普拉博沃·苏比安托 (Prabowo Subianto) 及其竞选搭档的资格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesian-court-rejects-first-two-petitions-seeking-election-re-run-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 06:52:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国、日本称朝鲜发射弹道导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-fires-missile-off-east-coast-south-korea-japan-say-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国军方表示，朝鲜周一向其东海岸发射了“数枚”短程弹道导弹，此举立即引起首尔的谴责，称其对朝鲜半岛的稳定构成严重威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-fires-missile-off-east-coast-south-korea-japan-say-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 06:25:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>所罗门群岛选举仍悬而未决，投票仍在继续</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/solomon-islands-election-balance-voting-continues-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[所罗门群岛选举因其对地区安全的影响而受到中国和美国的关注，这场选举正在演变为一场激烈的竞争，反对党赢得席位，独立人士掌握着组建下一届政府的关键。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/solomon-islands-election-balance-voting-continues-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 06:17:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>媒体称亲华党以压倒性优势赢得马尔代夫选举</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pro-china-party-wins-maldives-election-landslide-media-say-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[媒体周一称，马尔代夫选民让总统穆罕默德·穆伊祖的政党在议会选举中取得压倒性胜利，这一结果将使印度洋群岛更加接近中国，远离传统伙伴印度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pro-china-party-wins-maldives-election-landslide-media-say-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 05:50:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼央行首次降息推迟至第三季度，随着卢比贬值，今年降息幅度较小：路透调查</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/bank-indonesias-first-rate-cut-pushed-q3-smaller-cuts-this-year-rupiah-falls-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透调查发现，由于通胀上升，且美联储再次强硬立场导致卢比走软，印尼央行将在下季度和第四季度再次降息，降息时间晚于此前预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/bank-indonesias-first-rate-cut-pushed-q3-smaller-cuts-this-year-rupiah-falls-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 05:30:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南警方逮捕国会主席助理</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-police-arrest-national-assembly-chairmans-assistant-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[公安部周一表示，在长期开展的反腐败运动中，越南警方以滥用职权罪逮捕了国民议会主席助理范泰河。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-police-arrest-national-assembly-chairmans-assistant-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 05:23:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
